3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a Markov decision process to model the high-level decision problem, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the problem of controlling a robot to perform complex tasks, which is a core problem in systems and control. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - The paper proposes an algorithm for computing task and motion policies, which involves programming and algorithmic design.
